    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、僕のことを心配して探し回ってくれてたんだ\nなのにごめんね。条件反射でついビンタしちゃって",
      "startTime": 6.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや……俺の方こそ、葵を見つけた喜びのあまり\n浮かれ過ぎたよ。驚かせてすまない",
      "startTime": 14.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあお互い様ということで、この話は終わりだ\n仲直りの証に、次はパラセーリングをやってみようよ",
      "startTime": 22.0537180264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "モーターボートに引っ張ってもらって、海の上を\n飛ぶなんて、凄く楽しそうじゃない？",
      "startTime": 29.0537180264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "サーフィンもそうだけど、沖縄に来たら\n一度はやってみたかったんだよね",
      "startTime": 34.3203846931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそうだな。俺はここで見てるから\n葵だけやって来たら……",
      "startTime": 39.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、早くしないと日が暮れちゃうよ\n早く行こう、{user}君",
      "startTime": 43.4680026373,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cruise-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2500.002034599994,
          "startTime": 45.9680046719
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_wind-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2500.002034599994,
          "startTime": 45.9680046719
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2500.002034599994,
          "startTime": 45.9680046719
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、{user}くーん！\n僕が見えるー！？　パラセーリング、楽しいよー！",
      "startTime": 50.5680054348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "見えてるぞー、葵ー！　それにしても随分高くまで\n上がるんだな。あ、今度は右に旋回したぞ",
      "startTime": 62.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_wind-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3946.8489965000017,
          "startTime": 66.7135156632
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……結構激しく上下に揺れているぞ……\n今日は風が強いから、そのせいかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 70.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4584.9836669000015,
          "startTime": 75.2183170002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま。次は君の番だよ\n……って、なんで帰ろうとしてるの？",
      "startTime": 80.3849803608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　それは……パラセーリングも終わったし\nそろそろ旅館に帰ろうかなと……",
      "startTime": 86,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "君がまだやってないでしょ。楽しいからやろうよ\n大体、二人一緒に乗るのがどうしてダメなの？",
      "startTime": 92.6270238878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……ゴシップ誌の記者にでも撮られたら\n大変じゃないか",
      "startTime": 100.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "記者さんだって、こんな場所じゃバカンスしてるよ\n第一、そんなの撮られても僕は気にしないから",
      "startTime": 105.7662812236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ……万が一、俺の体重のせいで\nパラセールが落ちたら大変だろ……？",
      "startTime": 111.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "君の体重は何百キロあるの？\nそれに「じゃあ」って……今思いついた言い訳でしょ",
      "startTime": 117.5542399092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、怖がってる？\nふふっ、意外と可愛いところがあるんだね",
      "startTime": 124.6542399092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、君がパラセールに乗る時は、僕が隣で\n手を繋いであげようか？　それなら怖くないでしょ",
      "startTime": 132.6209065758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった、観念した。乗るよ\nそこまで言われちゃ俺も引き下がれないしな",
      "startTime": 140.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10900.000000000005,
          "startTime": 151.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "一人でも大丈夫だから、葵はここで俺の雄姿を\nカメラで記録しててくれ。じゃ、行ってくる",
      "startTime": 146.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "行ってらっしゃい。……親切で言ってあげたんだけどな\nそれじゃ、君の雄姿を撮影させてもらうよ",
      "startTime": 155.851626492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、インストラクターさん、ちょっといいかな？\n次のパラセーリングの参加者だけど、僕の友達でね……",
      "startTime": 163.5849669461,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.670989999994,
          "startTime": 168.8516379361
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cruise-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.670989999994,
          "startTime": 168.8516379361
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、葵ー！　見えてるかー！　なんだ\nやってみたら全然怖くない……うわっ！",
      "startTime": 175.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7948.35723189999,
          "startTime": 177.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4400.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 180.3666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7833.333333300005,
          "startTime": 183.8
        },
